Fruits and Their Sunlight Needs
Apple

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Banana

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Orange

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Grape

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Strawberry

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Pineapple

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Kiwi

Sunlight Need: Full sun to partial shade (4-6 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Peach

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Plum

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Cherry

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
Mango

Sunlight Need: Full sun (6-8 hours of direct sunlight daily)
